  x Warrior: Tank. Reduces incoming damage. Lots of blocking.
x Bolster (auto): Grant 8 block and removes 1 arousal. Being hit by a damaging action grants the caster 1 defensive momentum.
x Vice Grip (auto): Deals damage and taunts 2 enemies.
x Masochism (auto): Same as today
x Harden: Prevents block from falling off this turn, and grants your party major defense for 1 turn.

(test)  - Rogue: DPS. Deals damage and crits.
x Sneak Attack: Same as today.
x Exploit: Same as today.
x Combo Breaker: Deal 4 corruption damage and interrupts. Always critically hits if your target is charging an action.
x Advantage: Deal 4 corruption damage. Has a 10% crit chance per point of arousal your target has. 


(test)  - Cleric: Primarily heals by direct healing / healing over time. Easy to play. All heals are reactive.
x Heal. Same as today, minus the preventing block from falling off. Heal 4 HP plus another 10 multiplied by target's missing HP percentage.
x Radiant heal: Puts a healing over time spell on all players that also grants Major Blessing, increasing healing taken by 30%.
x Penance: Makes your healing abilities do damage this turn.
x Reserection. Fully heals a player. Can only be used once per combat. Free and instant cast. Can be used on defeated players.

(test)  - Tentaclemancer-  Tank (utility): Tanks by weakening enemies.
x Constrict: Deal 2 damage, taunt and add 1 arousal to up to 2 targets.
x Siphon: Heal yourself for an amount equal to 2x your target's arousal.
x Gag: Interrupts your target and prevents them from using ranged abilities for 1 turn. Adds 2 arousal.
x Restrain: Deal 2 damage and apply Major Weaken to up to 2 targets for 1 turn, reducing their damage done by 30%. 

(test)  - Monk: Healer - Heals by attacking
x Uplifting Strike - Same as now. Add an extra charge.
x(smartheal) Round Kick - Deals damage and heals a party member. Can be riposted.
x Chi Touch - Deals 4 damage to your target and grants you Major Mending for 2 turns.
x Gambling Strike - Deals 2 damage and grants the party 2 additional reroll. Can be riposted.

(test)  - Elementalist - DPS: Deal damage when enemies attack
x Backlash: Deal damage based on the nr of attacks used by an enemy last turn.
x Static Cling: Deals damage whenever your opponent uses an action for 2 turns.
x Kinetic Charge: Give an opponent Major Clumsy for 2 turns. When they miss, gain 3 offensive momentum.
x Divert: Deals heavy damage to an enemy that missed an attack last turn, and grants you 2 random momentum. 2 charges

  - Necromancer - Tank (offense) by doing damage and stealing health
vt Siphon : Deals damage and heals you for the amount.
vt Unholy Grasp: Taunt up to 2 targets for 1 turn. Each time they use an action, you gain 1 HP and 1 random momentum.
vt Leech: Deal 4 corruption damage and put Major Lifesteal on your target for 1 turn, giving any player attacking them 2 HP. 
vt Corrupt: All enemies take damage equal to their arousal, and heal you for the amount. Can be used twice per battle.

Arcanist - Healer (proactive)
vt Ward: Give a player 6 block. Unlimited charges.
x Shield: What earth shield does today.
vt Barrier: Grants your party 4 block and Major Defense for 1 turn, decreasing damage taken by 30%.
vt Embrace: Heals all players in your party for an amount equal to their block.

